# PLAYER::SUPPRESS_CRIME_THIS_FRAME

## Summary
Can be use to disable all instances of a crime type on this frame

## Parameters
* **PLAYER_INDEX** player
* **CRIME_TYPE** crimeToReport

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
crimeType: see REPORT_CRIME
